<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1"/>
  <meta name="description" content="Influence PRO — Gestão completa para micro influenciadores. Controle publis, agenda, metas e ganhe com indicações."/>
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#07070F"/>
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"/>
  <title>Influence PRO — Gestão para Micro Influenciadores</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#07070F; --surf:#0F0F1C; --border:#1A1A2E;
      --text:#EAE8F5; --sub:#6B6880;
      --ac:#7C6AF7; --ac2:#EC4899;
      --green:#34D399; --yellow:#FBBF24; --red:#F87171;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:16px;}
    body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}
    img{max-width:100%;display:block;}
    a{text-decoration:none;}
    ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px;}
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--ac);border-radius:2px;}

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav{
      position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;
      padding:14px 20px;
      display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
      background:rgba(7,7,15,.92);
      backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    }
    .nav-logo{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),var(--ac2));
      -webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
    }
    .nav-btn{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),#6366F1);
      border:none;border-radius:50px;
      padding:9px 18px;
      color:#fff;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;
      cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.3px;
      box-shadow:0 2px 14px rgba(124,106,247,.35);
      transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s;
      -webkit-appearance:none;
    }
    .nav-btn:active{transform:scale(.96);}

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero{
      min-height:100svh;
      padding:90px 20px 60px;
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;
      text-align:center;
      position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .hero-glow{
      position:absolute;width:340px;height:340px;
      background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(124,106,247,.18),transparent 70%);
      top:60px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .badge{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
      background:rgba(124,106,247,.12);border:1px solid rgba(124,106,247,.28);
      border-radius:50px;padding:5px 14px;
      font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ac);
      margin-bottom:24px;
      animation:up .5s ease both;
    }
    .bdot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:pulse 2s infinite;}
    @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.35}}
    h1{
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
      font-size:clamp(34px,10vw,52px);
      font-weight:800;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-1.5px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      animation:up .5s .08s ease both;
    }
    .gr{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff,var(--ac) 55%,var(--ac2));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;}
    .hero-p{
      font-size:15px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.72;
      max-width:340px;margin-bottom:34px;
      animation:up .5s .15s ease both;
    }
    .cta-row{
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;width:100%;max-width:320px;
      animation:up .5s .22s ease both;
    }
    .btn-main{
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),#6366F1);
      border:none;border-radius:50px;
      padding:16px 28px;
      color:#fff;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;
      cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.2px;
      box-shadow:0 4px 22px rgba(124,106,247,.42);
      transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s;
      -webkit-appearance:none;
    }
    .btn-main:active{transform:scale(.97);box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(124,106,247,.3);}
    .btn-out{
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;
      background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:50px;
      padding:14px 28px;
      color:var(--sub);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;
      cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .2s,color .2s;
      -webkit-appearance:none;
    }
    .btn-out:active{border-color:var(--ac);color:var(--text);}
    @keyframes up{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

    /* ── PHONE MOCKUP ── */
    .phone-wrap{
      position:relative;
      margin-top:50px;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;
      animation:up .7s .3s ease both;
    }
    .phone{
      width:230px;
      background:var(--surf);border-radius:34px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.65),0 0 0 1px rgba(124,106,247,.08),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      overflow:hidden;padding:16px 12px;
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;
    }
    .pn{width:60px;height:3px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;margin:0 auto 14px;}
    .pl{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:3px;text-align:center;line-height:1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),var(--ac2));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;}
    .ps{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:5px;color:var(--sub);text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;}
    .ph{background:rgba(124,106,247,.12);border:1px solid rgba(124,106,247,.18);border-radius:12px;padding:10px;margin-bottom:7px;}
    .ph-l{font-size:7px;color:var(--sub);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:2px;}
    .ph-v{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);transition:opacity .4s;}
    .ph-s{font-size:8px;color:var(--sub);}
    .pg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5px;margin-bottom:7px;}
    .pm{background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;padding:7px 8px;}
    .pm-v{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:800;}
    .pm-l{font-size:7px;color:var(--sub);}
    .pr-lbl{font-size:7px;color:var(--sub);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:5px;}
    .pr{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;padding:7px 8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:5px;}
    .pi{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:8px;font-weight:800;flex-shrink:0;}
    .pp{display:inline-flex;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:20px;font-size:6px;font-weight:700;}
    .pnav{display:flex;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:7px;margin-top:auto;}
    .pni{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:1px;font-size:6px;color:var(--sub);}
    .pni.on{color:var(--ac);}
    .pglow{position:absolute;bottom:-40px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:160px;height:80px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(124,106,247,.2),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;}

    /* ── STATS ── */
    .stats{
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;
      background:var(--border);
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .stat{
      background:var(--bg);padding:24px 18px;text-align:center;
    }
    .sv{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),var(--ac2));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;}
    .sl{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.4;}

    /* ── SECTIONS ── */
    .sec{padding:64px 20px;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;}
    .stag{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2.5px;color:var(--ac);margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase;}
    .sh{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,7vw,38px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .sp{font-size:14px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:40px;}

    /* ── FEATURES ── */
    .feat-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;}
    .feat{
      background:var(--surf);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;
      padding:20px;display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;
      transition:border-color .2s;
    }
    .feat:active{border-color:rgba(124,106,247,.3);}
    .fi{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .ft{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:5px;}
    .fd{font-size:13px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.65;}

    /* ── REFERRAL ── */
    .ref-sec{padding:64px 20px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,rgba(124,106,247,.04),transparent);}
    .ref-sec .sec{padding:0;margin:0 auto;}
    .lvls{margin-top:0;margin-bottom:32px;}
    .lvl{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:13px;
      padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:10px;
      transition:border-color .2s;
    }
    .lvl:active{border-color:rgba(124,106,247,.25);}
    .lpct{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;min-width:50px;}
    .ltx div:first-child{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;}
    .ltx div:last-child{font-size:12px;color:var(--sub);}
    .tree{background:var(--surf);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:20px;}
    .tn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-bottom:10px;}
    .tav{border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
    .earn{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:800;color:var(--green);}
    .total-row{border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:12px;padding-top:12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}

    /* ── PLANS ── */
    .plans-sec{padding:64px 20px;}
    .plans-sec .sec{padding:0;margin:0 auto;}
    .plan-cards{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;margin-top:40px;}
    .plan{background:var(--surf);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:22px;padding:28px;position:relative;}
    .plan.hot{border-color:var(--ac);background:linear-gradient(160deg,rgba(124,106,247,.07),rgba(99,102,241,.03));}
    .pbadge{position:absolute;top:-10px;right:16px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),#6366F1);color:#fff;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:9px;font-weight:800;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:1px;}
    .pname{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:5px;}
    .pprice{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:800;line-height:1;margin-bottom:3px;}
    .pprice span{font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--sub);}
    .pper{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);margin-bottom:20px;}
    .pdiv{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin-bottom:18px;}
    .pf{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:9px;font-size:13px;color:var(--sub);}
    .ck{color:var(--green);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .lk{color:var(--border);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;}
    .pbtn{
      display:block;width:100%;padding:14px;border-radius:50px;
      font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;
      text-align:center;cursor:pointer;margin-top:22px;
      transition:transform .15s;border:none;-webkit-appearance:none;
    }
    .pbtn:active{transform:scale(.97);}
    .pbtn.fr{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--sub);}
    .pbtn.pr{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),#6366F1);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(124,106,247,.4);}

    /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
    .testi-sec{padding:64px 20px;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;}
    .testi-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;margin-top:40px;}
    .testi{background:var(--surf);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:22px;}
    .stars{color:var(--yellow);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .tq{font-size:14px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.72;margin-bottom:16px;font-style:italic;}
    .ta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
    .tav{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),#6366F1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;font-size:12px;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
    .tn2{font-weight:700;font-size:13px;}
    .th{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);}

    /* ── CTA FINAL ── */
    .cta{padding:80px 20px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
    .cta-glow{position:absolute;width:400px;height:200px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(124,106,247,.1),transparent 70%);top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);pointer-events:none;}
    .cta h2{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,9vw,44px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.08;margin-bottom:18px;}
    .cta p{font-size:15px;color:var(--sub);margin-bottom:36px;line-height:1.7;}
    .cta-btns{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;max-width:320px;margin:0 auto;}

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer{
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      padding:28px 20px;
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:10px;
      text-align:center;
    }
    .f-logo{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ac),var(--ac2));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;}
    .ft{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);}

    /* ── SCROLL REVEAL ── */
    .rv{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity .6s ease,transform .6s ease;}
    .rv.on{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

    /* ── DESKTOP OVERRIDES ── */
    @media(min-width:640px){
      .cta-row,.cta-btns{flex-direction:row;justify-content:center;}
      .feat-list{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;}
      .plan-cards{flex-direction:row;}
      .plan{flex:1;}
      .testi-list{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;}
      nav{padding:18px 40px;}
      .nav-btn{font-size:13px;padding:10px 22px;}
      h1{font-size:clamp(44px,7vw,72px);}
      .sec{padding:90px 40px;}
      .ref-sec{padding:90px 40px;}
      .plans-sec{padding:90px 40px;}
      .stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);}
      .hero-p{max-width:460px;}
      .phone{width:260px;}
      .pl{font-size:26px;}
      .ph-v{font-size:24px;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">INFLUENCE PRO</div>
  <a href="https://andradeje86-collab.github.io/Influence-pro3" class="nav-btn" target="_blank">📱 Acessar Grátis</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="badge"><span class="bdot"></span>Para Micro Influenciadores</div>
  <h1><span class="gr">Gerencie sua</span><br/>carreira de<br/><span class="gr">influenciador</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-p">Controle publis, agenda, metas e ganhe dinheiro indicando amigos. Tudo em um app simples e poderoso.</p>
  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="https://andradeje86-collab.github.io/Influence-pro3" class="btn-main" target="_blank">📱 Acessar Grátis</a>
    <a href="#features" class="btn-out">Ver funcionalidades ↓</a>
  </div>

  <div class="phone-wrap">
    <div class="phone">
      <div class="pn"></div>
      <div class="pl">INFLUENCE</div>
      <div class="ps">PRO</div>
      <div class="ph">
        <div class="ph-l">FATURAMENTO TOTAL</div>
        <div class="ph-v" id="pv">R$ 2.880</div>
        <div class="ph-s">+ 3 permutas este mês</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pg">
        <div class="pm"><div class="pm-v" style="color:#FBBF24">4</div><div class="pm-l">Publis semana</div></div>
        <div class="pm"><div class="pm-v" style="color:#34D399">R$2,80</div><div class="pm-l">Ganhos ref.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr-lbl">ÚLTIMAS PUBLIS</div>
      <div class="pr">
        <div class="pi" style="background:rgba(248,113,113,.15);color:#F87171">FN</div>
        <div style="flex:1;min-width:0">
          <div style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis">FitNow Suplementos</div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:2px;margin-top:1px"><span class="pp" style="background:rgba(248,113,113,.2);color:#F87171">Reels</span><span class="pp" style="background:rgba(52,211,153,.2);color:#34D399">✓ postado</span></div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#34D399;flex-shrink:0">R$800</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr">
        <div class="pi" style="background:rgba(251,191,36,.15);color:#FBBF24">MV</div>
        <div style="flex:1;min-width:0">
          <div style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700">Moda Vibe</div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:2px;margin-top:1px"><span class="pp" style="background:rgba(248,113,113,.2);color:#F87171">Reels</span><span class="pp" style="background:rgba(251,191,36,.2);color:#FBBF24">⏳ pendente</span></div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#34D399;flex-shrink:0">R$1.200</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pnav">
        <div class="pni on"><span style="font-size:12px">⬡</span>Home</div>
        <div class="pni"><span style="font-size:12px">◈</span>Publis</div>
        <div class="pni"><span style="font-size:12px">◷</span>Agenda</div>
        <div class="pni"><span style="font-size:12px">◎</span>Metas</div>
        <div class="pni"><span style="font-size:12px">⬟</span>Rede</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pglow"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats rv">
  <div class="stat"><div class="sv">100%</div><div class="sl">Grátis para começar</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="sv">3</div><div class="sl">Níveis de indicação</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="sv">R$10</div><div class="sl">Plano Premium/mês</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="sv">∞</div><div class="sl">Publis no Premium</div></div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="sec" id="features">
  <p class="stag rv">Funcionalidades</p>
  <h2 class="sh rv">Tudo que você precisa<br/>para crescer</h2>
  <p class="sp rv">Do controle de publis à gestão de indicações — centralize sua carreira em um só lugar.</p>
  <div class="feat-list">
    <div class="feat rv">
      <div class="fi" style="background:rgba(251,191,36,.13)">📸</div>
      <div><div class="ft">Gestão de Publis</div><div class="fd">Registre cada publicação com marca, tipo, valor e status. Alertas automáticos de prazos.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat rv">
      <div class="fi" style="background:rgba(124,106,247,.13)">📅</div>
      <div><div class="ft">Agenda Inteligente</div><div class="fd">Calendário com check-list por postagem. Publis vão automaticamente para a data certa.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat rv">
      <div class="fi" style="background:rgba(52,211,153,.13)">🎯</div>
      <div><div class="ft">Metas Personalizadas</div><div class="fd">Defina e acompanhe metas de seguidores, faturamento e engajamento com progresso real.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat rv">
      <div class="fi" style="background:rgba(248,113,113,.13)">📣</div>
      <div><div class="ft">Alertas de Entrega</div><div class="fd">Aviso quando uma publi está vencendo hoje ou atrasada. Nunca perca um prazo.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat rv">
      <div class="fi" style="background:rgba(236,72,153,.13)">🧬</div>
      <div><div class="ft">Rede de Indicação</div><div class="fd">Indique amigos e ganhe em 3 níveis: 10%, 5% e 3%. Renda passiva recorrente.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat rv">
      <div class="fi" style="background:rgba(96,165,250,.13)">💸</div>
